Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:16.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134280,136199}Hey, is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143539,144457}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144457,145792}Quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:29.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145792,149462}He'll get better in no time,\Nhe just has to eat and rest enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:34.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149754,154634}I have no idea who he is, so I took the liberty\Nto take a peek at his belongings, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154634,156928}A vagabond, as expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:37.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156928,157929}Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169440,171359}So huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174320,176197}One. Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186833,189043}He's awake! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204267,205810}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205810,208771}So you came here looking for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:31.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208771,211774}Pardon my bluntness,\Nbut given your posture,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:34.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211774,214736}I can't imagine it would be\Ntoo difficult to land a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214736,216654}I mean, you're very muscular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218531,220324}It's not always a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220324,221242}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221242,222869}How is that not a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223619,225830}It just is. Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226414,227707}Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230752,232754}Well, all right, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244182,246350}What are you gonna do\Nfrom now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:11.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246768,251355}He will stay at our house for a while,\Nat least until he gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251355,253107}What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253107,254942}Is he going to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254942,257612}Once that time comes,\Nlet me think…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:22.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258070,262909}We'll have to find you a place to stay\Nif you're going to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262909,266329}Oh, don't be afraid. It'll be fine\Neven if you break a pickaxe or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266329,268164}All of our employees\Nare nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268164,270416}Don't worry about anything, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270416,271626}Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272210,273878}Ian Copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273878,275171}That's the big guy's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281385,282345}He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:46.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282345,286766}That's the half-dead guy\Nyou saved the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286766,288684}Yes. Something tells me\Nhe'll do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289477,291646}See what I'm talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291646,294482}"Do well"? An understatement\Nof the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:58.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294482,298861}Even if the cart is empty, it's still made of iron,\Nand he handles three of them all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304909,308663}You were right. What a strongman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308663,312667}His arms look like\Nthey're made of iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315336,317463}Hey! Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:22.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318673,322218}If you're finished with the carts,\Nbring the shovels in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322218,323261}Shovels?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323261,326681}They're in the boxes\Ninside the warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345741,348077}I brought the shovels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349537,351122}You brought\Nthe whole box at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352373,353624}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367930,370892}Gentlemen, I'm just flabbergasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:14.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371017,374437}He was told to bring the shovels\Nand brought all of them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:22.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376397,382194}There aren't many men in this world\Nwho can carry a weight like that so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382194,383696}Was it really that heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:24.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383696,384947}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391370,394957}So that Ian fellow, you're saying\Nhe's even bigger than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396167,398461}He's about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399170,400296}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400296,402465}Ian Copper, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402882,406761}Mr. Carraclough seems to\Nhave brought one hell of a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406761,409472}But he doesn't say much.\NIt's kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409764,413935}Well, with him around\Nour job will get so much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424612,427031}A big man who lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:11.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427031,431869}Found by a mine employee who's been\Nlooking after him for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431869,433287}There's a good chance\Nthat's our guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434246,435873}A good chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435873,437875}That's him, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437875,440586}Let's find a phone and report it\Nto the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440586,441295}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443047,444215}Hey, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444215,445091}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445091,447426}Is this car yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447426,448344}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448344,450471}But you have nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450471,452473}Are you guys merchants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452473,453683}Merchants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453683,455309}Oh? You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:39.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455309,459146}I'm asking because nobody comes\Nto our town apart from occasional peddlers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459146,461315}and I was wondering what\Nmerchandise we'd see this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463025,464443}– We are—\N– Walter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464443,465319}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465319,467655}We're on duty, we don't have\Nthe time to play with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467655,469323}I apologize, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:50.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469865,470866}On duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471409,473160}They're from the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474036,475705}Looks like something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475705,477373}{\i1}Here are news for this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:02.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478124,482962}{\i1}The criminal who has robbed\Nthe London Bank last Thursday is still at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:07.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483129,487091}{\i1}The investigators have expanded\Ntheir search coverage throughout England.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487091,489844}{\i1}They want to resolve\Nthe case as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490344,492471}{\i1}– As for the other news…\N{\i1}– They robbed a bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493055,494181}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494181,496017}That's right. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497768,500479}Thank you for your cooperation, sir.\NYou truly saved our skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500479,501230}Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501230,504358}The man we talked about earlier,\Nhe appears to have a record.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504358,505526}That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:30.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506068,510489}I've been catching criminals for 15 years.\NMy instincts have never let me down yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513784,516078}I determined where he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516162,518831}Let's watch him\Nfor a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:44.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518831,524086}I will not let a lousy bank robber like him\Nmock the British police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524420,525212}I'm with you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526297,528090}A bank robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534722,537892}There's a bank robber…\Nin our town?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540561,543022}What's wrong, girl?\NYou don't like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554366,555367}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556619,557578}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557578,558412}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565169,567171}It's the building to my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567588,568339}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571717,574970}Why are they heading\Ntowards the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575888,577765}No, Lassie!\NBad girl! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585231,586440}So this is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586440,589527}Yes. At least according\Nto the store clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:53.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589902,593114}But the lights are out.\NMaybe he's away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593114,594865}Quit yapping and observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594865,595574}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595574,597743}Wait, that's the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597743,599203}What are they looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600079,601205}The lights are on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601539,603082}That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:06.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603082,606168}Learn to use your eyes and ears\Nbefore your goddamn mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606168,607044}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607044,609713}Well, well.\NIt's finally working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610297,612591}We almost ran out of matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612591,613634}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614051,615970}Are you sure I can live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:19.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615970,619723}Unfortunately, it's a little gloomy here,\Nbut you can stay here for as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:21.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620891,621725}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623018,624520}One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:29.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624520,629441}About the food, I told the store owner,\NRichard Jones, about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629441,631610}He'll come here with\Nsome food later this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631610,632528}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632528,635990}If you need anything,\Njust let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635990,637783}I'll see what I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637783,638742}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639326,641328}He looks just like our criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:42.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641829,642746}All right, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643289,645249}My instincts are never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646333,649253}And they tell me he's our guy.\NNo doubt about it.
Comment: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:53.63,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:653632,653632}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660848,662057}Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:02.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662057,662933}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663350,665144}About Ian…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665144,668063}Ah, yes, I'm so glad\Nhe started to work with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669231,671734}What do you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671734,673152}What's going on, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673152,675070}You're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675070,676572}Is something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676572,678199}Well, how to put it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678199,680201}You mean how he's so taciturn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:24.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680201,684455}I think I'm a man of few words myself,\Nso I can't really talk, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:29.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684455,689627}Compared with me,\NIan seems to be even more silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:35.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689627,695966}Maybe that is why I want to help him\Nfind his way in our community.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:37.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697009,697593}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:41.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697593,701138}Heh, he might be a bit strange, I admit.\NBut he's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702181,705851}Of all the people\NI have met in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:49.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705851,709230}I think Ian is the most even-tempered\Nand good-natured person so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709855,712107}Even if he is reserved,\Nhe's strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:56.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712107,716987}Some people get scared by these qualities\Nand misjudge his character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717696,719615}It's tough to be misjudged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722243,723535}I guess Dad's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:08.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724578,728916}Maybe the police officers\Ndid misjudge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731210,733921}But if he robbed a bank…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735297,736674}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:20.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736674,740427}The police are going to\Ninvestigate this, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740427,742429}I mean, that's why they're here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745516,746934}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747309,750479}What if Ian really is a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751563,753941}Dad will be so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760406,762032}He's not going anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762032,764201}Of course he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764201,767329}He thinks this place\Nis a prefect hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767329,770541}He's not going to\Ngive himself away so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770541,773544}Are we going to watch him\Nuntil he slips up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773544,775129}We'll help him slip up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:55.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775129,775921}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775921,778340}I'm leaving the stakeout\Ntomorrow to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779174,780718}What about you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781510,782845}Well, just watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782845,785347}I'm going to smoke him out\Nof this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:24.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803907,804867}Good morning, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804867,806201}Good morning, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806201,807328}Morning, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807328,808620}Good morning, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810331,811915}Good morning, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825262,828265}He really is one incredible fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829641,831268}Ian Copper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831643,833771}Did he do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:14:00.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834188,840652}No, not really. He just happens to look a bit\Nlike the man the London Police is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840652,843781}Surely you're not referring\Nto the bank robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:07.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844198,847493}I heard that this man\Nis quite a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847493,848660}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:13.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848660,853916}Any job is better than staying\Nin prison like he used to, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853916,855167}Prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855167,856919}Oh, I said a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856919,858087}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868847,870682}A man like that\Nis working in the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870682,873769}Does your husband\Nwork in the mine, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873769,874686}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874686,876355}I'd be concerned, if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879775,880943}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880943,882694}John? John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884738,887741}You agreed to pick up some berries\Ntoday with us, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887741,889535}Ah… I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889535,891870}Something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895207,896500}What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896500,897418}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917855,919606}He's going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928323,929616}Where is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932327,934329}I can't believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955434,957186}Looks like he lost track of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959438,960898}Lassie? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962149,964401}Where are you going, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967654,968655}Ian...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975287,976914}Ah! A knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981585,984338}Did the police come\Nto your house as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984338,986715}Yes. They scared my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:30.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987007,990177}Do you really think\Nhe could be the bank robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:33.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990177,993680}We can only speculate, but it sure\Ngives you a lot to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993680,995224}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007736,1009905}Did you gentlemen know\Nthat he's an ex-convict?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009905,1010697}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:54.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010697,1014117}I shudder to think he's brought\Nsome criminal into our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014117,1015369}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016537,1018914}I heard he served time in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019248,1021875}What was Mr. Carraclough\Nthinking, giving shelter to—?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021875,1022876}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024545,1026338}Did my Dad do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026338,1028882}No, nothing at all, son.\NNever mind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031385,1032636}Welcome back, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032636,1033262}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033554,1036306}We need to talk, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036306,1037599}It's about Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038976,1040894}Ian's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040894,1044273}He worked very hard today,\Nso I invited him to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050445,1052114}It's heaven in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052114,1055200}Of course it is.\NI put all of my skill into this meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055534,1057035}Would you like another bowl, Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057661,1058537}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058787,1059955}What's up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059955,1061290}You're awfully quiet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061290,1062040}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063875,1064585}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065377,1066253}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066253,1067379}Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067379,1068213}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068213,1071800}After you left, the manager\Nmade a lot of ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072259,1074886}He has lost his gold watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074886,1078348}Mr. Carraclough! What were you thinking,\Nbringing a guy like him to our town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078348,1081393}Now he's stolen the manager's watch?\NThat's going way too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081393,1082477}"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082477,1084771}I'm talking about Ian!\NThe ex-convict!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086189,1088984}What are you talking about,\Ngentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090527,1092529}Ian was here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092529,1093530}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093530,1095073}Anyway, let's talk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099953,1102372}What exactly do you claim Ian did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103040,1105125}I take that you heard it\Nfrom the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:29.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105125,1109296}I heard from Grandma Forrest that they're\Ngoing all over the town spreading rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109880,1111798}They're watching us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118597,1119806}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119806,1122601}It appears you suspect\NIan of some criminal act.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122601,1124436}Do you have any evidence for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:49.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124436,1129024}We would appreciate if you would leave\Nsuch matters to the professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129024,1131068}So you do not have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131526,1133904}Otherwise you would\Nhave arrested him long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133904,1136740}What are you thinking,\Nspreading bad rumors of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136740,1138784}What will you do if he is innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138784,1141203}I am perfectly fine with\Nyour investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141203,1144373}But I will not tolerate spreading\Nany slander in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144373,1145415}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147584,1149127}You gentlemen go to your homes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150170,1151588}– Dad.\N– Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151588,1153757}I… I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153757,1155592}I saw Ian holding a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155592,1158136}I know about it.\NIt was among his belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158136,1159179}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159680,1162140}John, you also have a knife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162140,1163725}The one I gave to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165477,1166186}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166770,1167938}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170148,1173944}Get a testimony from these people\Nregarding the stolen gold watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174194,1175904}Yes sir. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175904,1177280}Get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177280,1178865}Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179282,1181952}For Christ's sake.\NEven a watch thief will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181952,1183370}I'm going to arrest them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184413,1186373}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187833,1189084}I've been thinking, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:54.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189334,1194423}Even if we don't know the truth yet,\Nwe have to trust Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194423,1197592}I mean, Dad believes\Nin him so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198385,1199803}What's going on, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199803,1201388}I'll be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202556,1204391}Wait up, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:06.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206184,1206893}It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209020,1212107}What is the police doing here\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212107,1214609}Hasn't your boss come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214609,1215402}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:18.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215402,1218405}Can we wait here\Nfor him to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218947,1220407}I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:23.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220407,1223410}You can wait in the manager's office.\NThe door is unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:28.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225036,1228915}His name is Dohan. What questions\Ndo you think we should ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229833,1230667}Sir!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233295,1234588}We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234588,1236298}This is strictly against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236298,1238925}Shut your mouth. The man\Nin the next room might overhear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239634,1241428}Hey! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265327,1267162}I figured it'd be\Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267162,1268663}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268663,1270457}Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:13.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270457,1273752}It was here all along, all right.\NThat idiot forgot he put it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273752,1275670}We shouldn't have bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301112,1304199}Perfect. I'll let them know\Nwe have found the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:47.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304199,1307118}No. That will be unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:47.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307118,1307869}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:53.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310747,1313917}I will get him jailed,\Nno matter the methods.
