Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:05.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321842,1325262}{\i1}Apparently he stole the gold watch\Nfrom the mine's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325262,1327556}{\i1}I know he's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327556,1330809}{\i1}Lassie, I'm sure\Nthere's something more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330809,1333645}{\i1}Next episode:\N"Proving Ian's Innocence".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333645,1335146}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
